name: Yūhi ga kireidesu ne.
description:
夕日が綺麗ですね。
The sunset is beautiful, isn't it?

It's mean the way someone explain to other participate that "I love you, but I'm letting you go" just some romantic phrase to tell.

Sunset will always be beautiful for us to enjoy anytime, right? but we can't see it for a long time or can be said to be momentary pleasure. Just like loving someone, we can't force them to stay with us no matter how beautiful the story that happened between us. "Deep"
